# App knowledge (ASA)

**Hub:** [docs/APP_KNOWLEDGE/README.md](docs/APP_KNOWLEDGE/README.md)

On any non-trivial task in this repo:

1. Read the hub (and the relevant domain doc under `docs/APP_KNOWLEDGE/domains/`).
2. Use the matching `.agents/skills/asa-*` skill for the area you edit.
3. Before finishing, update knowledge if you learned invariants, pitfalls, CI/deploy truth, or new key files — plus a dated line in [docs/APP_KNOWLEDGE/CHANGELOG.md](docs/APP_KNOWLEDGE/CHANGELOG.md).

Cross-project maintenance protocol: personal skill `maintain-app-knowledge` in `~/.cursor/skills/`.

End substantial replies with **Knowledge update** (learned / updated files / gaps).
